{
  "page": "Vaes Qosar",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Essos.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Vaes Qosar is located in Essos\"><img alt=\"Vaes Qosar is located in Essos\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/300px-Essos.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"284\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/450px-Essos.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/600px-Essos.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 80.6%; left: 95.8%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Vaes Qosar\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: -6.5em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Vaes Qosar</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\"><a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> west of the <a href=\"/index.php/Bone_Mountains\" title=\"Bone Mountains\">Bone Mountains</a> and the location of Vaes Qosar\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Vaes Qosar</b> is a ruined <a href=\"/index.php/Qaathi\" title=\"Qaathi\">Qaathi</a> city located in <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>, east of <a href=\"/index.php/Qarkash\" title=\"Qarkash\">Qarkash</a> and northwest of <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a>, in the southeastern portion of the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_waste\" title=\"Red waste\">red waste</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiaf_central_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiaf_central_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It was originally called <b>Qolahn</b>, but it is now known by its <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_language\" title=\"Dothraki language\">Dothraki language</a> name, Vaes Qosar, meaning City of Spiders, after its destruction by the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Century_of_Blood\" title=\"Century of Blood\">Century of Blood</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_beyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_beyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vaes_Qosar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vaes_Qosar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> and her <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khalasar\" title=\"Khalasar\">khalasar</a></i> pass the ruins of Vaes Qosar while traveling from <a href=\"/index.php/Vaes_Tolorro\" title=\"Vaes Tolorro\">Vaes Tolorro</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafjourneys.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafjourneys.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vaes_Qosar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiaf_central_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiaf_central_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  Central Essos.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiaf.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiaf.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_beyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_beyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=